  "enArticles": [
    {
      "id": "1",
      "language": "en",
      "title": "The Road Not Taken",
      "content": [
        "Two roads diverged in a yellow wood,",
        "And sorry I could not travel both",
        "And be one traveler, long I stood",
        "And looked down one as far as I could",
        "To where it bent in the undergrowth;"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "2",
      "language": "en",
      "title": "A Bright Day",
      "content": [
        "The sun rises gently over the horizon,",
        "Painting the sky in hues of gold and blue.",
        "Birds sing their morning melodies,",
        "Welcoming another beautiful day.",
        "Every moment is a fresh beginning."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "3",
      "language": "en",
      "title": "Learning to Code",
      "content": [
        "Programming is not about typing,",
        "It is about thinking and solving problems.",
        "Every bug is an opportunity to learn,",
        "Every feature is a chance to create.",
        "Keep practicing, keep improving."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "4",
      "language": "en",
      "title": "The Art of Persistence",
      "content": [
        "Success is not final, failure is not fatal.",
        "It is the courage to continue that counts.",
        "Every setback is a setup for a comeback.",
        "The path to greatness is paved with persistence.",
        "When you feel like quitting, remember why you started.",
        "Dreams do not work unless you do.",
        "The only way to fail is to give up.",
        "Your struggle today builds your strength for tomorrow.",
        "Keep pushing forward, one step at a time.",
        "The view from the top is worth every step of the climb."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "5",
      "language": "en",
      "title": "Digital Age Reflections",
      "content": [
        "In this digital age we live and breathe,",
        "Technology connects us across the globe.",
        "Screens light up our daily lives,",
        "Information flows at lightning speed.",
        "Yet we must not forget the simple joys,",
        "A walk in nature, a heartfelt conversation,",
        "The warmth of a smile, the touch of a hand.",
        "Balance is key in this modern world,",
        "Embrace the new but cherish the old,",
        "For in harmony we find true fulfillment.",
        "Let us navigate this digital landscape wisely,",
        "Using tools to enhance, not replace our humanity.",
        "The future is bright for those who adapt,",
        "While staying grounded in what truly matters."
      ]
    }
  ],
